{"tid":838802,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓樂壇一大創舉！防彈少年團登紐約聯合國大會演講 表現得體氣勢過人獲一致好評　","createTime":"2018-09-27T11:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T05:26:46.000Z","uid":9573,"like":25,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"130916e77bf9d4ceadb02c8f89c82b718cbcdc1f","tid":838802,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T11:43:26.000Z","msg":"南韓防彈少年團（BTS）到紐約出席聯合國大會演講，成為南韓樂壇一大創舉，同時最大的焦點就是，擔任演講的隊長RM全程以英文演說，表現得體氣勢過人獲不少好評，不過有粉絲發現看似超自信的RM，事實上拿演講稿的手抖個不停。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/26/1560678-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F1560678-XXL.jpg&h=cc2f32b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲南韓防彈少年團BTS受邀至聯合國大會演講。<br />\n<br />\nRM以隊長身分代表演說「通過全球領導力和責任分擔，建設和平、平等與可持續社會」近7分鐘的內容，RM以流暢英文、斷句頓點鏗鏘有力、眼神自信且堅定，很難讓人相信他完全沒有在海外生活，英文完全是靠自學而成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/26/1560693-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F1560693-XXL.jpg&h=475b9a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲RM以隊長身分全英文進行演講，粉絲發現他手狂顫抖。<br />\n<br />\n不過其實RM非常地緊張，他用手勢來掩飾顫抖的晃動，吹輕微至和緩偏東風。直到右手倚靠在桌上，顫抖狀況才改善。粉絲們紛紛對他上台臨危不亂，沉穩的表現深感佩服「不看手抖的話，還真看不出來緊張！」、「氣場真強。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/yoongsvixen/status/1044302094839279617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyoongsvixen%2Fstatus%2F1044302094839279617&d=0SoPDjFcrTt7RNAzShIFEUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=cee44fe0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyoongsvixen%2Fstatus%2F1044302094839279617&h=f69e3fc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/yoongsvixen/status/1044302094839279617</a><br />\n▲防彈少年團RM在聯合國進行演講，粉絲發現他手狂顫抖。"},{"pid":"98392d7c31e283b723297602a6eeeea8529ccf16","tid":838802,"uid":1748,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T11:45:06.000Z","msg":"冇朱千雪相嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3564e5bca44f1b119b56bd0a7f8e5cd2094f426c","tid":838802,"uid":63057,"like":10,"dislike":12,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T11:45:28.000Z","msg":"泡狗食屎啦"},{"pid":"09cb525e621d51282d7c2a20d4721f579c06c2b6","tid":838802,"uid":63057,"like":17,"dislike":10,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T11:46:06.000Z","msg":"屌那星，條友好撚樣衰"},{"pid":"0affdff7136294930e38e533029b0f13625d61df","tid":838802,"uid":69038,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"呢班人有過咩大貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b753c0638fbb8cc3386eadb4c9f2bca033f337","tid":838802,"uid":168366,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T11:47:26.000Z","msg":"成堆死lar形"},{"pid":"6ee7d7a7dac5c509ded8c84401e6e863be8fc188","tid":838802,"uid":197093,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"0affdff7136294930e38e533029b0f13625d61df","tid":838802,"uid":69038,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"呢班人有過咩大貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"就係唔撚知，屌，高錕都未上，佢地上撚乜野"},{"pid":"2a760ada28f5026186282948ba344ec3ce7d958d","tid":838802,"uid":2471,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T11:48:31.000Z","msg":"防彈少年係做依d?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n5O3gvEVvlI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dn5O3gvEVvlI&d=0SoPDjFcrTt7RNAzShIFEUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=cf8d0456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n5O3gvEVvlI</a>"},{"pid":"20a254ab12be0468ab7945ab10a9e3c9816a425e","tid":838802,"uid":124630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T11:48:37.000Z","msg":"吹輕微至和緩偏東風<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /